channel.title: Log in problem
channel.description:
The game loads fine and I can click things but I can't type anything.
I've tried chrome, mozilla, and internet explorer, same with all of them. I cleared the cache, uninstalled and reinstalled java, along with the JRE. Also restarted the computer and the web browsers with no success. I have no idea what else to try, any suggestions?
